{"title":"Readers’ Rides: Will’s Albatross RD-00 Builder’s Special Road Bike","link":"https://theradavist.com/albatross-bikes-rd-00-builders-special-road-bike/","date":1682078424000,"content":"<p><em>We get many submissions for our weekly Readers’ Rides feature. Some range from parts bin basket bikes to framebuilders’ own creations. This week’s feature comes from the latter. Will from <a href=\"https://www.albatrossbikes.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Albatross Bikes</a> sent in his personal <a href=\"https://www.albatrossbikes.com/projectgallery/rd00-builders-special\" target=\"_blank\">RD-00 Builder’s Special</a>, along with some process imagery and the bike’s geometry, so let’s get to it!</em><span></span></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1440\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,576&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1125&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?resize=768,432&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1013&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,751&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?resize=700,394&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,864&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_48b-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1152&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1094\" height=\"646\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Frame-Geo.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Frame-Geo.jpg?w=1094&amp;quality=75 1094w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Frame-Geo.jpg?resize=1024,605&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Frame-Geo.jpg?resize=768,453&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Frame-Geo.jpg?resize=700,413&amp;quality=75 700w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2325\" height=\"1692\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?w=2325&amp;quality=75 2325w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?resize=1024,745&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?resize=2000,1455&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?resize=768,559&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?resize=1800,1310&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?resize=1335,972&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?resize=700,509&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?resize=1536,1118&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_RAW.jpg?resize=2048,1490&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>I built this bike to be a quick-handling and comfortable everyday road bike. I had an older 10spd SRAM Red groupset on the shelf and decided to build up the bike with a “Modern Classic” theme. Rim brakes, mechanical shifting, and with 10 gears in the back and a derailleur for the front chainrings (gasp!) come together for a rock-solid, reliable build that can be pulled off the rack and ridden at any time. Minimal maintenance required!</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_08-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_09-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_21-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1920\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,768&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1500&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?resize=768,576&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1350&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,1001&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?resize=700,525&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1152&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00_Seatmast_assembly-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1536&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Other details I worked into the build were a custom-machined seatmast topper with an internal wedge to maintain the very clean aesthetic I was looking for. The rear rim brake was also mounted to the seattube to reduce the loads on the seatstays and let me reduce their size without getting any flex issues when on the brakes.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_45-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_38-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_30-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Lastly, the routing for the rear brake was designed to accommodate a rear brake on the left lever in a nod to my motorcycling past.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?fit=1024,9999&amp;quality=75\" alt srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?w=2560&amp;quality=75 2560w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?resize=1024,683&amp;quality=75 1024w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?resize=2000,1333&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?resize=1800,1200&amp;quality=75 1800w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?resize=1335,890&amp;quality=75 1335w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?resize=700,467&amp;quality=75 700w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2023/04/RD00-WH_28b-scaled.jpg?resize=2048,1365&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<h3>Build Specs:</h3>\n<p>Frame: Albatross Bikes RD00<br />\nFork: Whiskey No.7 Road Fork<br />\nHeadset: Cane Creek 40<br />\nStem: FSA Vdrive 100mm<br />\nHandlebar: Custom Specialized Aerofly 40cm<br />\nPedals: Time XPRO 10<br />\nBB Praxis: T47 M30<br />\nCrank: Praxis Zayante<br />\nChainring: Praxis 50/34 X-Ring<br />\nChain: 10spd SRAM Red<br />\nRear Derailleur: 10spd SRAM Red<br />\nShifters: 10spd SRAM Red<br />\nCassette: 10-28 PG-1070<br />\nWheels: Rolf Prima Vigor<br />\nTires: Donnelly Strada LGG 700×28<br />\nBrakes: SRAM Red<br />\nSaddle: PRO Stealth Performance<br />\nSeatpost: Albatross Bikes Prototype<br />\nBar Tape: Easton Microfiber<br />\nBottle Cages: Albatross Bikes Prototype</p>\n<p> </p>\n<hr />\n<p> </p>\n<p><em>We’d like to thank all of you who <a href=\"mailto:readersrides@theradavist.com\" target=\"_blank\">submitted Readers Rides</a> builds to be shared here at The Radavist. The response has been incredible and we have so many to share over the next few months. Feel free to submit your bike, listing details, components, and other information. You can also include a portrait of yourself with your bike and your Instagram account! Please, shoot landscape-orientation photos, not portrait. Thanks!</em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/albatross-bikes-rd-00-builders-special-road-bike/\">Readers’ Rides: Will’s Albatross RD-00 Builder’s Special Road Bike</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"af575c182eef84c468ea931d20fabe4398ab21721a0846cb169c17ce380253f2","category":"Cycling"}